     3	/**
     4	 * NPD PACKAGING stage — `deletePackagingComponent` write Server Action.
     5	 *
     6	 * Org-scoped delete of a packaging component. Wrapped in withOrgContext (RLS as
     7	 * app_user). RBAC: requires `npd.packaging.write`. Writes an audit_log row in
