     2	
     3	/**
     4	 * NPD HANDOFF stage — `getHandoff` read Server Action.
     5	 *
     6	 * Reads the (single, per-project) handoff checklist + its line items + the
     7	 * destination-BOM facts surfaced on the screen (destination_bom_code, the
     8	 * project's product code/SKU, promote_to_production_date, the destination
     9	 * warehouse name, and the factory-release linkage if the project was already
    10	 * released). Org-scoped via withOrgContext → RLS engaged with
    11	 * app.current_org_id(). RBAC read gate = `npd.handoff.read` (BYTE-IDENTICAL to
    12	 * the seeded permission string in migration 236).
    13	 *
    14	 * No mocks, no hard-coded rows. `ready` (the green "Ready to promote" bar) is
    15	 * derived here as "every checklist item is checked" so the screen never
    16	 * re-derives the gate.
    17	 */
